---
title: Crispy Sea Bass with Sticky Roasted Cauli and Potatoes
description: This delicious Crispy Sea Bass has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crispy-sea-bass-20ada48f-fd793714.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/crispy-sea-bass-61c349424e76fa0b9962af2e-bd8e7d2f.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/crispy-sea-bass-61c349424e76fa0b9962af2e
